org.miloss.fgsms.presentation

Interface IProxyLoader

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProxyLoader, ProxyLoaderCXF

    public interface IProxyLoader
    Proxy Loader interface used for web applications accessing fgsms services

    This interface is used by the class ProxyLoader and serves as an abstraction layer to support multiple soap stacks
    Author:
    AO
